{"tid":985702,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[求屌醒]Plan緊6月頭中亞 去過請入","createTime":"2019-01-17T23:42:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-27T23:55:27.000Z","uid":228704,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"44d94357de41457a480b71862a82e883c13e8ab1","tid":985702,"uid":228704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T23:42:53.000Z","msg":"比啲背景資料先：舊年4月去完哈薩克 不過淨係跟團去左almaty 同astana 。而家同上次freelance請個嗰guide叫佢幫下手，中亞人做野好撚慢<br />\n我應該唔會嬲嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">濃縮版去邊：香港 - 哈薩克 (2-3日) - 土庫曼 (4-5日) - 烏茲別克 (5日) - 吉爾吉斯+哈薩克 (15 日) </span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nDay 1：air Astana 直航 almaty $4200 晏晝到咗hea吓食埋飯返酒店<br />\n<br />\nDay 2：我諗著day trip big almaty lake或者喺alamty鳩行下算 會唔會唔夠時間？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nDay 3：問題嚟喇：呢日係星期四，諗著飛入Ashgabat。turkmenstein airline 個網寫話有機但系問極個guide都係同我講話呢啲機位只可以土庫曼啲旅行社買到同得星期五先有機?? 另外website寫話$295eur 一個 佢報俾我 $230usd一個🤷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n搭星期五機 : day3就系almaty鳩hea吓, 之前個日去big almaty lake<br />\n<br />\n搭星期四機： 凌晨四點起飛 7am 到ashgabat <br />\n<br />\nDay 4: 晏晝飛去ashgabat 或者 (如搭禮拜四) city tour / underground lake<br />\n<br />\nDay 5: Ashgabat day tour / 去underground lake<br />\n<br />\nDay 6：去地獄之門 夜晚 瞓街🙋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nDay 7：睇埋日出緊著開車去烏茲別克過境 預足成日夜晚係khiva瞓 個guide話同我book系city wall入面酒店: 50usd 兩個人<br />\n<br />\nDay 8 :日頭khiva day tour 夜晚去 Urgench 搭飛機去Bukhara 夜晚9半起飛 飛個幾鐘到<br />\n夜晚訓bukhara<br />\n<br />\nDay 9: Bukhara day tour<br />\n<br />\nDay 10 : 日頭繼續 Bukhara city 夜晚7點上火車去Andjian 準備入吉爾吉斯<br />\n<br />\nDay 11 : 晏晝1點到 Andjian 諗著Fergana valley day tour 可以嘅順手入埋吉爾吉斯<br />\n<br />\nDay 12: meet up 個guide<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n跟住個啲未plan到🤦 大概諗著喺karakol almaty附近行下山 無咩興趣入Bishkek 最尾留返日係almaty買野<br />\n<br />\n去過嘅ching add我tg放吓料呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/Sonyma9fan\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FSonyma9fan&d=e09FmYdHwEhMRyOr1dZ1nkbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=9c60ca61\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/Sonyma9fan</a>"},{"pid":"56c60685bad2668f253acf7deb82915cc4c4014f","tid":985702,"uid":228704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"44d94357de41457a480b71862a82e883c13e8ab1","tid":985702,"uid":228704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T23:42:53.000Z","msg":"比啲背景資料先：舊年4月去完哈薩克 不過淨係跟團去左almaty 同astana 。而家同上次freelance請個嗰guide叫佢幫下手，中亞人做野好撚慢<br />\n我應該唔會嬲嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">濃縮版去邊：香港 - 哈薩克 (2-3日) - 土庫曼 (4-5日) - 烏茲別克 (5日) - 吉爾吉斯+哈薩克 (15 日) </span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nDay 1：air Astana 直航 almaty $4200 晏晝到咗hea吓食埋飯返酒店<br />\n<br />\nDay 2：我諗著day trip big almaty lake或者喺alamty鳩行下算 會唔會唔夠時間？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nDay 3：問題嚟喇：呢日係星期四，諗著飛入Ashgabat。turkmenstein airline 個網寫話有機但系問極個guide都係同我講話呢啲機位只可以土庫曼啲旅行社買到同得星期五先有機?? 另外website寫話$295eur 一個 佢報俾我 $230usd一個🤷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n搭星期五機 : day3就系almaty鳩hea吓, 之前個日去big almaty lake<br />\n<br />\n搭星期四機： 凌晨四點起飛 7am 到ashgabat <br />\n<br />\nDay 4: 晏晝飛去ashgabat 或者 (如搭禮拜四) city tour / underground lake<br />\n<br />\nDay 5: Ashgabat day tour / 去underground lake<br />\n<br />\nDay 6：去地獄之門 夜晚 瞓街🙋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br